---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  description="River Williams Psychotherapy — Somatic and EMDR therapy for adults navigating trauma, anxiety, and life transitions."
>
  <Hero />

  <!-- Intro section -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-20">
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Replace with River's actual introductory copy — 2–3 paragraphs, warm and grounded in tone, emphasizing somatic approach and relational presence -->

    <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-slate text-base leading-[1.85]">
      <p>
        Therapy, at its best, is not only a conversation — it is a place where the body's
        accumulated wisdom is finally given room to speak. If you've found yourself stuck in
        cycles of anxiety, grief, or trauma responses that talk alone hasn't been able to touch,
        you're not alone, and you're not broken.
      </p>
      <p>
        River works from the understanding that healing happens relationally, somatically, and
        at the pace your nervous system allows. Sessions weave together EMDR, somatic
        experiencing, and psychodynamic awareness to help you build safety in your own body
        and create lasting change — not just symptom management.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're navigating a specific trauma history, a major life transition, or a
        quieter sense that something isn't quite right, this practice offers a steady, curious,
        and non-judgmental space to explore that.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-5 mt-12">
      <a href="/about" class="btn-primary">Learn about River</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">View services &amp; rates</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visual divider before footer -->
  <div class="w-full h-px bg-sand max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6"></div>
</Layout>
